title: “Obscuritas” Now on Display at Blackbird Cafe
text:
Written by Blackbird Cafe Last Updated on 19 October 2015 
Right now at Blackbird Café, catch the fantastic work of Emilio Saylor, award winning and published tattoo artist. His exhibit “Obscuritas” showcases charcoal and pencil sketches in intricate frames. Each piece is unique and signed by Emilio. 
Emilio works at Umbrella Ink Tattoo Studio in Valparaiso. His artwork is whimsical, dark, and full of great detail. You can find his artwork not only on the walls of Blackbird, but on the bodies of many individuals in Northwest Indiana. 
Check out Emilio’s profile on Umbrella Ink’s website via this link: http://umbrellainktattoo.com/emiliosaylor 
The “Obscuritas” pieces displayed at Blackbird Café are available for purchase. Ask any friendly Blackbird associate for details. Blackbird Cafe
